==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Icebound
<hw>Ice"bound`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Totally surrounded
with ice, so as to be incapable of advancing; <as>as, an
<ex>icebound</ex> vessel</as>; also, surrounded by or fringed with ice
so as to hinder easy access; <as>as, an <ex>icebound</ex>
coast</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>icebreaker</ent>⟦br⟧
